Tipo quando você pega
duas bolas

00:07:15.730 --> 00:07:18.182
de sorvete de cookies
com granulado extra

00:07:18.183 --> 00:07:20.177
na sorveteria
Mason Family...

00:07:20.178 --> 00:07:22.815
- no Happy Harbor, Rhode Island.
- no Happy Harbor, Rhode Island.

